### ping api
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ping
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "message": "hello"
}

### get user info
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/get-user-info
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}


### get user credits
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/get-user-credits
